description:
Katherine has proven her humility and obedience to whomever she may be
asked to service, pleasing the men of the Order. As a result, she’s brought to
the chambers of the infamous Seed Bearer. Katherine’s tasted cock for the
first time, and now she’s eager to have more. She’s heard rumors of his
appetites and wonders what he’ll demand of her. The readies herself to be
washed and anointed, determined to make him happy.
title: Sister Katherine Washing
